#  To install docker
```
 sudo   yum    install   docker
 ```
 #  to start  docker  
 ```
  sudo  systemctl  start  docker
  sudo  systemctl  status   docker
  ```
  # some basic docker commands 
  ```
    8  sudo  docker   search   java 
    9  sudo  docker   search   hadoop
  14  sudo  docker   images
   15  sudo  docker   pull  java
   16  sudo  docker   pull  alpine
   17  sudo  docker   images
```
